Sometimes called 'RP' Trooper, '''arpitroopers''' were the designation for ground based infantry forces that were deployed into battlefields through the use of [[Repulsor pack/Legends|repulsor packs]], in effect becoming a form of [[Clone paratrooper/Legends|paratroopers]]. These soldiers were used during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and were common among local planetary militias, like the [[Balawai]] [[Balawai militia|militia]].

